25827F9F.Line10.ED393: Without my friend here, I don't think I would have made it. You've helped me find home again. Thank you, and farewell.

4460A722.Line4.ED90F: The swamp doesn't harm what it thinks belongs to it.

5D71D84F.Line1.ED393: She's infected. I don't know why, but I've heard they're not bothered by anything out here.

78499A26.Line8.ED90F: I've been here, waiting, all these years. I never thought you'd come back, but to hear your voice again... that's all I've ever wanted.

DE550814.Line6.ED393: You'll hear it every day, mother. I won't leave you, not again.
